snippet: The American Jessica Korda shot a five-under 68 to take a two-stroke lead through the second round of the Reignwood Classic in Beijing.
abstract: American golfer Jessica Korda takes second-round lead at Reignwood Classic in Beijing; other golf news noted.

headline.main: Korda in Lead at Reignwood Classic
